                            </p>

                            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Why Sealing Air Leaks Is Important
                            </h2>
                            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                                Sealing air leaks isn’t just about comfort—it’s one of the most cost-effective home
                                improvements you can make. According to the U.S. Department of Energy, sealing leaks can
                                save up to 20% on heating and cooling costs annually.
                            </p>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-6 space-y-2">
