                                <li>Reduced noise: Seals act as sound barriers.</li>
                            </ul>

                            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Common Mistakes to Avoid</h2>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-6 space-y-2">
                                <li>Applying caulk on dirty or wet surfaces.</li>
                                <li>Using the wrong type of caulk (interior vs. exterior).</li>
                                <li>Sealing over old caulk without removing it.</li>
                                <li>Overfilling gaps with foam (it expands and can damage trim).</li>
                            </ul>

                            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Conclusion</h2>
